Summary:	Tiny CD distro
Summary(pl.UTF-8):	Mała dystrybucja na CD
Name:		emovix
Version:	0.9.0
Release:	1
Epoch:		1
License:	GPL
Group:		Applications
Source0:	http://dl.sourceforge.net/movix/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	a96492f338824b24c5a9e714c57eddcf
